data.description: Lone Oak ISD! This stunning home is situated in a subdivision with NO HOA, offering an open floor plan with a spacious kitchen, featuring ample cabinets, an electric stovetop, and a large island overlooking the living area with a cozy stone, wood-burning fireplace. The primary suite is located at the back of the home for added privacy, featuring a luxurious spa-like bathroom with a resort-style shower and soaking tub, tall vanities, and a large walk-in closet. The secondary bedrooms are also spacious, perfect for guests or hobbies. With a generous lot size, there is plenty of outdoor space for hosting barbecues, playing games, or gardening and includes gated access to the 18x24 shop with electricity and a single roll up garage door. High speed fiber internet is also available and already connected to the house. Laundry room refrigerator will convey.  Don't miss this opportunity to own a stunning property!
